[907.897595, "o", "\u001b[16;1H\u001b[17;1H\u001b[7m-----Info: (coreutils)chmod invocation, 120 lines --39%-----------\u001b[0m\u001b[1;1H\u001b[K\u001b[2;1H   If used, MODE specifies the new file mode bits.  For details, \u001b[2;66H\\\u001b[3;1Hsee the\u001b[K\u001b[4;1Hsection on \u001b[4m*note File permissions\u001b[24m::.  If you really want MODE to \u001b[K\u001b[4;66H\\\u001b[5;1H\u001b[K\u001b[5;1Hhave a\u001b[6;1Hleading ‘-’, you should use ‘--’ first, e.g., ‘chmod -- -w file’.\u001b[7;1HTypically, though, ‘chmod a-w file’ is preferable, and ‘chmod -w \u001b[7;66H\\\u001b[8;1Hfile’\u001b[K\u001b[9;1H(without the ‘--’) complains if it behaves differently from what \u001b[9;66H\\\u001b[10;1H‘chmod\u001b[K\u001b[11;1Ha-w file’ would do.\u001b[12;1H\u001b[K\u001b[13;1H   The program accepts the following options.  Also see \u001b[4m*note Com\u001b[24m\u001b[K\u001b[13;66H\\\u001b[14;1H\u001b[4mmon\u001b[24m\u001b[K\u001b[15;1H\u001b[4moptions\u001b[24m::.\u001b[K\u001b[16;1H\u001b[K\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2;66H\\\u001b[4;66H\\\u001b[7;66H\\\u001b[9;66H\\\u001b[13;66H\\\u001b[16;1H"]
[907.930015, "o", "\u001b[16;1H\u001b[17;1H\u001b[7m-----Info: (coreutils)chmod invocation, 120 lines --40%-----------\u001b[0m\u001b[1;1H   If used, MODE specifies the new file mode bits.  For details, \u001b[1;66H\\\u001b[2;1Hsee the\u001b[K\u001b[3;1Hsection on \u001b[4m*note File permissions\u001b[24m::.  If you really want MODE to \u001b[K\u001b[3;66H\\\u001b[4;1H\u001b[K\u001b[4;1Hhave a\u001b[5;1Hleading ‘-’, you should use ‘--’ first, e.g., ‘chmod -- -w file’.\u001b[6;1HTypically, though, ‘chmod a-w file’ is preferable, and ‘chmod -w \u001b[6;66H\\\u001b[7;1Hfile’\u001b[K\u001b[8;1H(without the ‘--’) complains if it behaves differently from what \u001b[8;66H\\\u001b[9;1H‘chmod\u001b[K\u001b[10;1Ha-w file’ would do.\u001b[11;1H\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H   The program accepts the following options.  Also see \u001b[4m*note Com\u001b[24m\u001b[K\u001b[12;66H\\\u001b[13;1H\u001b[4mmon\u001b[24m\u001b[K\u001b[14;1H\u001b[4moptions\u001b[24m::.\u001b[K\u001b[15;1H\u001b[K\u001b[16;1H‘-c’\u001b[16;1H\u001b[1;66H\\\u001b[3;66H\\\u001b[6;66H\\\u001b[8;66H\\\u001b[12;66H\\\u001b[16;1H"]
