[914.237097, "o", "\u001b[16;1H\u001b[17;1H\u001b[7m-----Info: (coreutils)touch invocation, 173 lines -- 3%-----------\u001b[0m\u001b[1;1H‘touch’ changes the access and/or modification timestamps of the\u001b[2;1Hspecified files.  Synopsis:\u001b[K\u001b[3;1H\u001b[K\u001b[4;1H     touch [OPTION]... FILE...\u001b[5;1H\u001b[K\u001b[6;1H   Any FILE argument that does not exist is created empty, unless\u001b[6;66H\\\u001b[7;2Hoption\u001b[K\u001b[8;1H‘--no-create’ (‘-c’) or ‘--no-dereference’ (‘-h’) was in effect.\u001b[9;1H\u001b[K\u001b[10;1H   A FILE argument string of ‘-’ is handled specially and causes \u001b[10;66H\\\u001b[11;1H‘touch’\u001b[K\u001b[12;1Hto change the times of the file associated with standard output.\u001b[13;1H\u001b[K\u001b[14;1H   By default, ‘touch’ sets file timestamps to the current time.\u001b[15;1HBecause ‘touch’ acts on its operands left to right, the resulting\u001b[16;1Htimestamps of earlier and later operands may disagree.\u001b[K\u001b[16;1H\u001b[6;66H\\\u001b[10;66H\\\u001b[16;1H"]
[914.268488, "o", "\u001b[16;1H\u001b[1;1Hspecified files.  Synopsis:\u001b[K\u001b[2;1H\u001b[K\u001b[3;1H     touch [OPTION]... FILE...\u001b[4;1H\u001b[K\u001b[5;1H   Any FILE argument that does not exist is created empty, unless\u001b[5;66H\\\u001b[6;2Hoption\u001b[K\u001b[7;1H‘--no-create’ (‘-c’) or ‘--no-dereference’ (‘-h’) was in effect.\u001b[8;1H\u001b[K\u001b[9;1H   A FILE argument string of ‘-’ is handled specially and causes \u001b[9;66H\\\u001b[10;1H‘touch’\u001b[K\u001b[11;1Hto change the times of the file associated with standard output.\u001b[12;1H\u001b[K\u001b[13;1H   By default, ‘touch’ sets file timestamps to the current time.\u001b[14;1HBecause ‘touch’ acts on its operands left to right, the resulting\u001b[15;1Htimestamps of earlier and later operands may disagree.\u001b[K\u001b[16;1H\u001b[K\u001b[16;1H\u001b[5;66H\\\u001b[9;66H\\\u001b[16;1H"]
