[920.473344, "o", "\u001b[16;1H\u001b[1;1H     here.\u001b[2;1H\u001b[K\u001b[3;1H‘-f’\u001b[4;1H     Ignored; for compatibility with BSD versions of ‘touch’.\u001b[5;1H\u001b[K\u001b[6;1H‘-h’\u001b[7;3H-no-dereference’\u001b[8;1H     Attempt to change the timestamps of a symbolic link, rather \u001b[8;66H\\\u001b[9;1Hthan\u001b[K\u001b[10;1H     what the link refers to.  When using this option, empty file\u001b[10;66H\\\u001b[11;1Hs are\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H     not created, but option ‘-c’ must also be used to avoid warn\u001b[12;66H\\\u001b[13;1Hing\u001b[K\u001b[14;1H     about files that do not exist.  Not all systems support chan\u001b[14;66H\\\u001b[15;1Hging\u001b[K\u001b[16;1H     the timestamps of symlinks, since underlying system support \u001b[16;66H\\\u001b[16;1H\u001b[8;66H\\\u001b[10;66H\\\u001b[12;66H\\\u001b[14;66H\\\u001b[16;66H\\\u001b[16;1H"]
[920.505254, "o", "\u001b[16;1H\u001b[17;1H\u001b[7m-----Info: (coreutils)touch invocation, 173 lines --51%-----------\u001b[0m\u001b[1;1H\u001b[K\u001b[2;1H‘-f’\u001b[3;1H     Ignored; for compatibility with BSD versions of ‘touch’.\u001b[4;1H\u001b[K\u001b[5;1H‘-h’\u001b[6;3H-no-dereference’\u001b[7;1H     Attempt to change the timestamps of a symbolic link, rather \u001b[7;66H\\\u001b[8;1Hthan\u001b[K\u001b[9;1H     what the link refers to.  When using this option, empty file\u001b[9;66H\\\u001b[10;1Hs are\u001b[K\u001b[11;1H     not created, but option ‘-c’ must also be used to avoid warn\u001b[11;66H\\\u001b[12;1Hing\u001b[K\u001b[13;1H     about files that do not exist.  Not all systems support chan\u001b[13;66H\\\u001b[14;1Hging\u001b[K\u001b[15;1H     the timestamps of symlinks, since underlying system support \u001b[15;66H\\\u001b[16;1Hfor\u001b[K\u001b[16;1H\u001b[7;66H\\\u001b[9;66H\\\u001b[11;66H\\\u001b[13;66H\\\u001b[15;66H\\\u001b[16;1H"]
